<HEAD>Share Prices Open Lower, Edge Up</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Share prices opened slightly lower in London today
as traders reacted to Wednesday's fall in New York.
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index opened down
2.6 points at 1,745.5, but by 9:45 a.m. was back up to Wednesday's
close of 1,748.1.
