   The stock market declined slightly today in
sluggish trading.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 1.98 to 1,999.01
in the first half hour.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 7 to 6 in the early tally of
New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 466 up, 552 down and
