<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Prices on the London Stock Exchange fell Thursday
after a weak early trend on Wall Street compounded earlier worries
about inflationary pressure on the British economy.
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-stock index closed down
12 points, or 0.69 percent, at 1736.1.
