economic data that pointed to increased inflationary pressure on
the economy. The figures revived worries of a further increase in
base lending rates.
   The market was especially concerned by an increase in bank
lending last month.
   Share prices fell to the day's low during the afternoon because
of a weak early trend on Wall Street, dealers said.
